@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### 1. Ping Server
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/api/ping HTTP/1.1

### 2. Get All Auth Actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/api/auth/actions HTTP/1.1

### 3. Get All Resources
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/api/auth/resources HTTP/1.1

### 4. Get All Policies
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/api/auth/policies HTTP/1.1
